msgid "Recurrence tab"
msgstr "Gentagelses tidsrum"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some events take place regularly. You can specify their exact scheduling "
"here."
msgstr ""
"Nogle begivenheder gentages på en regulær måde. Du kan angive deres "
"nøjagtige skemalægning her."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1296
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<screeninfo>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s Edit Event dialog - Recurrence "
